name: P2P2P #3
description: This work is part of the P2P2P collection, which stands for Pixel to Print to Pixel. It is an exploration of what happens when you add an analog aspect to what is normally an all-digital workflow. Each work has gone through the same process of starting as Photoshop Bitmaps, followed by working with a Xerox copier back to being digitised and animated in After Effects.
